        friends and light candles in front of the idol of Jesus Christ. Churches are decorated with fairy lights and
        candles. People also create fancy Christmas cribs and adorn them with gifts, lights, etc. Children sing
        Christmas carols and also perform various skits marking the celebration of the auspicious day. One of the famous
